import nltk
nltk.download('punkt')
nltk.download('stopwords')
nltk.download('wordnet')

content=[]
from nltk.tokenize import sent_tokenize, word_tokenize
text = df.loc[:,'Содержание']
print(text)
for i in text:
    content.append(word_tokenize(i, language="russian"))
print(content)

In [21]:
new_content=content
from nltk.stem import SnowballStemmer
snowball = SnowballStemmer(language="russian")
for x in range(0,len(new_content)):
    for y in range(0,len(new_content[x])):
        ss = new_content[x][y]
        new_content[x][y]=snowball.stem(ss)
new_content

stop_words = stopwords
filtered_str=[]
new_content2=[]
for x in range(0,len(new_content)):
    for y in range(0,len(new_content[x])):
        filtered_str=' '.join((filter(lambda s: s not in stop_words,new_content[x])))
    new_content2.append(filtered_str)
new_content2

In [15]:
new_content=content
from nltk.stem import SnowballStemmer
snowball = SnowballStemmer(language="russian")
for x in range(0,len(new_content)):
    for y in range(0,len(new_content[x])):
        ss = new_content[x][y]
        new_content[x][y]=snowball.stem(ss)
In [16]:
stop_words = stopwords
filtered_str=[]
new_content2=[]
for x in range(0,len(new_content)):
    for y in range(0,len(new_content[x])):
        if new_content[x][y]=='xxx':
            new_content[x][y]=' '
        filtered_str=' '.join((filter(lambda s: s not in stop_words,new_content[x])))
    new_content2.append(filtered_str)
